@ActuatorApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5140

@ActuatorApi_ManagementAddress = http://localhost:5140
#@ActuatorApi_ManagementAddress = http://localhost:9999

### Get the default day-count forecast starting from today
GET {{ActuatorApi_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

###  Get the default day-count forecast starting from a certain date
GET {{ActuatorApi_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast?fromDate=9/1/2024
Accept: application/json

###  Get a specified-number-of-days forecast starting from today
GET {{ActuatorApi_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast?daysCount=2
Accept: application/json

### Get all forecast data
GET {{ActuatorApi_HostAddress}}/AllForecastData
Accept: application/json

### ACTUATORS
### Hypermedia (list all actuators)
GET {{ActuatorApi_ManagementAddress}}/actuator
Accept: application/json

### Beans actuator, list registered services ("Beans" comes from the Spring world)
GET {{ActuatorApi_ManagementAddress}}/actuator/beans
Accept: application/json

### DB Migrations actuator, list pending and applied database migrations
GET {{ActuatorApi_ManagementAddress}}/actuator/dbmigrations
Accept: application/json

### Env actuator, list environment/configuration sources and data
GET {{ActuatorApi_ManagementAddress}}/actuator/env
Accept: application/json

### Info actuator
GET {{ActuatorApi_ManagementAddress}}/actuator/info
Accept: application/json

### Health actuator
GET {{ActuatorApi_ManagementAddress}}/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

### Health actuator, check a specified group of contributors
GET {{ActuatorApi_ManagementAddress}}/actuator/health/readiness
Accept: application/json

### Loggers actuator, list all loggers
GET {{ActuatorApi_ManagementAddress}}/actuator/loggers
Accept: application/json

### Loggers actuator, update logging level for a logger
POST {{ActuatorApi_ManagementAddress}}/actuator/loggers/Microsoft.AspNetCore.Cors.Infrastructure.CorsMiddleware
Accept: application/json
{
  "configuredLevel": "TRACE"
}

### HTTP Exchanges actuator
GET {{ActuatorApi_ManagementAddress}}/actuator/httpexchanges
Accept: application/json

### Mappings actuator, list registered HTTP routes
GET {{ActuatorApi_ManagementAddress}}/actuator/mappings
Accept: application/json

### Metrics actuator, list all metrics
GET {{ActuatorApi_ManagementAddress}}/actuator/metrics
Accept: application/json

### Metrics actuator, check a meter
GET {{ActuatorApi_ManagementAddress}}/actuator/metrics/clr.process.uptime
Accept: application/json

### Prometheus endpoint, list all metrics
GET {{ActuatorApi_ManagementAddress}}/actuator/prometheus
Accept: application/json


### Refresh actuator, refresh application configuration
POST {{ActuatorApi_ManagementAddress}}/actuator/refresh
Accept: application/json

### Thread dump actuator
GET {{ActuatorApi_ManagementAddress}}/actuator/threaddump
Accept: application/json

### Heap dump actuator
GET {{ActuatorApi_ManagementAddress}}/actuator/heapdump
Accept: application/json
